Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.60,0:01:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.47,0:01:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽過世後已經一年半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.78,0:01:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.18,0:01:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但仍能像這樣感受到這藍天白雲及徐徐微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種幸福的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.62,0:01:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是草摩家的所有人常陪伴在身旁所賜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.99,0:01:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的媽呀!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.09,0:01:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,底…紙袋的底破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.53,0:01:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 我來幫妳撿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.77,0:01:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼好意思麻煩妳這位素昧平生的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.37,0:01:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 人有困難時應該互相幫助啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.74,0:02:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個超會給周遭找麻煩的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.48,0:02:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.38,0:02:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我光是呼吸都會給人造成困擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.22,0:02:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紙袋之所以會破就是在警告我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.96,0:02:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不該如此厚臉皮跑去紫吳哥家拜訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.16,0:02:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇!!對不起!!我跟全世界的人道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.87,0:02:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該來拜訪的！對不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.84,0:02:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是…利津嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.11,0:02:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的媽呀!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.01,0:02:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,素昧平生的人居然知道我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.91,0:02:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可見我早就惡名昭彰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我卻毫不知情還活得這麼悠栽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.29,0:02:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也向跟我同名的人說聲對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.62,0:02:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.49,0:02:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津的登場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是難得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.36,0:02:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,個性軟弱的利津會主動來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.47,0:03:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.54,0:03:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在您家門口給小透添了麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.67,0:03:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 一點也不麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.11,0:03:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興認識妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.08,0:03:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.15,0:03:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是女性吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.52,0:03:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.05,0:03:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津是我以前在溫泉旅館時受到照顧的老闆娘之女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.36,0:03:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳跟老闆娘長得太像了 所以我一眼就認出妳來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.60,0:03:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了 利津是十二生肖的猴子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.94,0:03:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我的孩子也是被十二生肖的猴怪所附身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.61,0:03:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是利津為何突然跑來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.11,0:03:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 造成你的困擾了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.18,0:03:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.89,0:03:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.89,0:03:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙妳的啦 跟妳開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的個性跟妳媽還真像呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都快出社會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為人處世得學著穩重點才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我叫草摩利津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前些日子家母承蒙妳的照顧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.04,0:04:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 我才是呢 我叫本田透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.37,0:04:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這是我的點心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.74,0:04:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼 送我的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.14,0:04:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.94,0:04:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來想買水果送你們但又不知道你們愛吃什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.38,0:04:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以決定買水果的書送你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.25,0:04:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 對不起 你不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起!原諒我!!我馬上去買水果!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.39,0:04:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.66,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 你就坦白跟我說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.47,0:04:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是個沒資格來你家拜訪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.60,0:04:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了沒這回事的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.11,0:04:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是嘛 我真的好想認識妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.34,0:04:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說妳來家裡玩 我是真的真的很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是從家母那邊聽說妳的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.56,0:05:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以好想見妳一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 不過還是很高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笑起來更是個大美女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.30,0:05:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家裡有客人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.07,0:05:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希好久不見了 對不起 打擾你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是那身打扮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上脫掉就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果真還是那副德性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.72,0:05:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津 妳沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.02,0:05:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.86,0:05:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡茶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.49,0:05:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳別忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.09,0:05:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.13,0:05:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得利津能鼓起勇氣來找我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就對她好一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津是來見小透的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.01,0:05:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了 雖然上次見過伯母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她近況還好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.18,0:05:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來也不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.55,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.38,0:06:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希愈看愈像阿綾哥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.12,0:06:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你慢坐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.99,0:06:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是說了不該說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.89,0:06:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我就是話多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.69,0:06:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不自覺的情況下給周遭人帶來不悅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.63,0:06:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.60,0:06:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒錯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.03,0:06:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 讓大家感到不悅 我馬上失陪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.74,0:06:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 打擾了這麼久 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.01,0:06:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼行呢 妳才剛來啊 怎麼可以走呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還沒招呼妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼敢當 請妳別這麼客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.92,0:06:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我自己想招待妳 妳再坐一會兒嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說我哪承當得起呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到妳這麼說我就心滿意足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又何必這麼說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.79,0:06:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.49,0:06:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 妳有沒有受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.06,0:06:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 倒是利津她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我居然在別人家裡打破茶杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.11,0:06:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我簡直是惡魔的化身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我打破的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.04,0:07:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.34,0:07:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不該來拜訪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.05,0:07:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉 我跟全世界的人道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津 危險！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.79,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明是女生 為何會變身…呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇咧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血…血！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.87,0:07:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.87,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 耶～？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.20,0:07:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此 小透受傷了 有空就過來看看她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.51,0:07:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上去也行嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.44,0:07:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.38,0:07:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥今天怎麼這麼好說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.45,0:07:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會偷偷愛上小透了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被我猜中了嗎 你好壞 好死相喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的有夠白痴的 我懶得跟你說啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.09,0:07:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說利津是個男孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.73,0:07:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但從以前就男扮女裝捨棄男兒身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.40,0:08:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊 我還認定她是女生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 包紮好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.11,0:08:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.61,0:08:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是他為何要男扮女裝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.31,0:08:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說男扮女裝感覺上比較安心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看利津就知道他很內向吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.52,0:08:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果打扮成男生看起來會更沒魄力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.45,0:08:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了 利津人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.16,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 上帝 神明 請懲罰我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.73,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危…危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他什麼時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.50,0:08:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這種事不是道歉就能了事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害妳受重傷真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有受重傷 只是小擦傷罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.85,0:08:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢說出自己是男兒身這件事也要跟妳道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.42,0:08:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我實在很丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.38,0:08:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 原來他也知道丟臉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.95,0:08:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得一點也不丟臉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還很適合你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.33,0:09:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小透 這種安慰話好像有點畫蛇添足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.10,0:09:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為何…為什麼老是闖禍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老給周遭人製造困擾、帶來麻煩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.34,0:09:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 也不是現在才發生這種狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.17,0:09:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣的人活在世上到底有什麼意義呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.81,0:09:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我是個毫無用處的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然還死皮賴臉的活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真恨這樣的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.59,0:09:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆…乾脆…像我這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.46,0:09:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不配活在這個世界上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我又沒那個勇氣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不需要的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.80,0:09:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不需要那種勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.84,0:09:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人就是因為活著…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.37,0:09:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為活著才會有喜怒哀樂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.38,0:09:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能出生到這個世上也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腳扭到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是有夠死皮賴臉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.94,0:10:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.91,0:10:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.64,0:10:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只聽說小透受傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.41,0:10:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 真抱歉 波鳥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.58,0:10:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 發生了許多事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.59,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的傷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是手擦傷罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.99,0:10:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且由希已經幫我包紮 沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.40,0:10:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.66,0:10:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 還讓你專程來一趟 真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.27,0:10:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話我想在這裡過夜 不知道可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.75,0:10:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是難得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.98,0:11:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你今天會說出這麼積極的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.82,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.72,0:11:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼利津跟波鳥會在家裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.83,0:11:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣過了三天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.23,0:11:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津常好像想說什麼似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.40,0:11:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但終究還是什麼話也沒說 每天只知道發呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.34,0:11:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鹽巴的量可以嗎 會不會太鹹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.58,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 剛剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.08,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧 羨慕吧 我的新婚妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.19,0:11:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續這麼胡扯下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當心被踢到屋頂去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 你也在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.16,0:11:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰是誰的新婚妻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不閉上你的爛嘴 當心我扭斷你的脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽呀 阿夾好兇喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.07,0:11:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣死我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.84,0:11:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安 阿夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.84,0:11:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳別只會笑 要懂得拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為這樣 那個白癡才會得寸進尺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說些五四三的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因妒忌而遷怒 實在太遜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.68,0:12:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.22,0:12:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波鳥 你為何還在這裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.55,0:12:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為波鳥在此 利津的傷勢才康復得這麼快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.12,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事跟我無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 牛奶沒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.49,0:12:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 沒了嗎 我馬上去買
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.83,0:12:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 不用這麼麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.67,0:12:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行呢 廚房一切由我負責
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻犯這麼大的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 非常對…對不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我早上都吃玉米片加牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.38,0:12:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才把阿夾的牛奶給喝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪大惡極的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.38,0:12:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你儘管懲罰我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.82,0:12:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懲罰我吧～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.86,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔 你也還在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.99,0:12:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 因為我拜託紫吳哥讓我住這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.26,0:12:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且本來只說住一晚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻兩晚、三晚一天天增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不但如此早上還吃玉米片加牛奶 真是任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.33,0:13:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津 拜託你別端著牛奶跑好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.11,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請別客氣 這盤牛奶給你喝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死都不喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.71,0:13:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我到底該如何是好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.05,0:13:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只需馬上去買瓶牛奶回來就行了 白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.02,0:13:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.62,0:13:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由希 今天睡過頭了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害你睡過頭了 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.16,0:13:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害你遲到了 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.53,0:13:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.63,0:13:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為遲到的關係害你被退學 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我早就教過你了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正義永遠會贏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.24,0:13:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰是正義來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.78,0:13:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就某個角度而言紫吳也是惡魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.05,0:13:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了 凡事學著沉著穩重點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.68,0:13:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家並不會特別在意你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你老跟大家道歉 大家也很困擾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.22,0:13:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子 這麼殘酷的話也能輕鬆脫口而出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.63,0:14:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也想當個堂堂男子漢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.33,0:14:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然 我好想有一天能像阿綾哥那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.04,0:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 這是無法達成的夢想嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.41,0:14:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為阿綾的自信心超出人類的常規
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.41,0:14:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先不提綾女的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 周遭人不像你想像中的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.22,0:14:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會責罵你也不會怪你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多給自己一點空間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.39,0:14:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.89,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對…我想說的就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.43,0:14:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少瞎掰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.46,0:14:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.57,0:14:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 對不起 爸 媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.92,0:14:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.18,0:14:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我笑得那麼甜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.49,0:15:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我老覺得他在責怪自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.53,0:15:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如同由希跟阿夾那樣 還有其他的草摩家人那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.46,0:15:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷責怪自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.03,0:15:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是為了什麼活在這個世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.04,0:15:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真高興有生下小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.58,0:15:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為有小透 我才能每天都活得這麼開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.88,0:15:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我是為了見媽媽才出生到人世間來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.62,0:15:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是這樣就開心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.93,0:15:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要！不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.23,0:15:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 原諒我 你饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.70,0:15:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上買新的章魚燒來 你饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.17,0:15:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不該拿回來的 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.57,0:15:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟世上的所有人道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利津…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說紫吳嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.25,0:16:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說不吃章魚燒就沒有靈感寫小說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.28,0:16:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.39,0:16:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 小透妳想說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 你先說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行呢 妳先說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.70,0:16:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼好意思先說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.93,0:16:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.07,0:16:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續這麼客套下去可能誰都別想說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.47,0:16:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說還是你先說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.88,0:16:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有事想請問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.95,0:16:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳上次和家母見面時有沒有聽說些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.89,0:16:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說覺得我讓她感到丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.33,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真抱歉 我這麼問妳 妳也會感到很困擾啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.40,0:16:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.10,0:16:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我這個兒子不肖 害她這麼抬不起頭來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.17,0:16:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個沒出息的小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.44,0:17:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然被附身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.58,0:17:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但又不像其他十二生肖的人那麼有才華
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.85,0:17:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是在運動或課業上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.62,0:17:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不比別人多付出一倍以上的努力就會跟不上大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.52,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 真抱歉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到草摩家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.06,0:17:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然出了我這種恥辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.59,0:17:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為此父母只能不斷跟大家道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.13,0:17:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我發現到只要男扮女裝就會感到安心點時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.33,0:17:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就開始男扮女裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.80,0:17:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但沒想到卻因此害父母增加跟人道歉的次數
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.08,0:17:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想振作起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也想恢復男兒身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還是沒有自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.66,0:17:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因這樣才更不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.59,0:17:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的胸口有如針扎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.77,0:18:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實爸媽也不想跟人道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.30,0:18:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們多想有個不會害他們老跟人磕頭道歉的兒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.37,0:18:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若能有個好兒子就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.98,0:18:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.28,0:18:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定沒有我還比較好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出生的存在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.89,0:18:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是沒有意義的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算相信是有意義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.97,0:18:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻也一點一點遺失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.54,0:18:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我卻仍賴活著 實在有夠死皮賴臉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.68,0:18:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以找得到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.21,0:18:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出為何會出生的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.22,0:18:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.75,0:18:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…因為事實上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.03,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想世上應該沒有人一開始就知道自己為何會出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.10,0:19:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.31,0:19:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都得靠自己的力量去尋找這個答案吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何會出生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何會活著 絕對有它存在的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.42,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想這些都得靠自己去尋找出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.72,0:19:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比方說活在夢想、工作、人群中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.16,0:19:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己尋找答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.43,0:19:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來或許很曖昧不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.67,0:19:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能會因此失去某些東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.97,0:19:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但還是希望知道原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.21,0:19:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要還活著 我也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.11,0:19:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且能的話 我希望能走進人群
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從別人身上尋找到這個意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.06,0:20:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了別人而活的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.09,0:20:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望別人能對我說他願意接納我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時也會覺得很沮喪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.00,0:20:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我會繼續加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.47,0:20:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.71,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以無所謂的 就算死皮賴臉也無妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為 人能死皮賴臉的活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.72,0:20:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表示他活得很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.56,0:20:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想再聽一次這番話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.10,0:20:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好希望妳再說一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.94,0:20:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的我也能找到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.21,0:20:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何會活著的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.44,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若能找到就好了 我想遲早應該能找到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.95,0:21:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也希望自己有朝一日能為別人而活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.52,0:21:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若能跟那個人一起吃章魚燒那就更開心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.33,0:21:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.40,0:21:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日 想跟某個人一起吃章魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.20,0:21:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也希望能說出自己是為了誰而出生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.18,0:21:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這句話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.61,0:21:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有某人等著我跟他說那就更好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.89,0:21:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得趕快把章魚燒帶回去給紫吳哥吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.19,0:21:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.06,0:21:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紫吳哥說一吃章魚燒就會變身為戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.96,0:21:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.90,0:21:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用章魚燒的那股力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.60,0:21:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
